<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Terminerinnerung</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }
        .email-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }
        .icon {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .icon svg {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            stroke: white;
            stroke-width: 2;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            stroke-linejoin: round;
            fill: none;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #111827;
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .highlight-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff 0%, #dbeafe 100%);
            border: 2px solid #bfdbfe;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .date-time {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1e40af;
        }
        .action-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin: 8px 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 32px;
            margin-top: 32px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                    <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"></line>
                    <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"></line>
                    <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"></line>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h1>Terminerinnerung</h1>
        </div>

        <p>Hallo {{ userName }},</p>
        <p>
            Dies ist eine freundliche Erinnerung an Ihren bevorstehenden Termin:
        </p>

        <div class="highlight-box">
            <div class="date-time">ðŸ“… {{ formattedDateTime }}</div>
            {% if sourceName %}
                <div style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e40af; margin-top: 8px;">{{ sourceName }}</div>
            {% endif %}
            {% set reservationExtras = reservation.getExtras() %}
            {% if reservationExtras|length %}
                <div style="margin-top: 16px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid #bfdbfe;">
                    <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #3b82f6; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px;">Inkl. Extras:</div>
                    {% for item in reservationExtras %}
                        {% set extra = item.extra %}
                        {% set quantity = item.quantity %}
                        <div style="font-size: 14px; color: #1e40af;">
                            {{ extra.title }}{% if quantity > 1 %} ({{ quantity }}x){% endif %}
                        </div>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>

        {% if isVirtual %}
        <div style="background-color: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #166534;">ðŸŽ¥ Virtuelles Meeting</p>
            <p style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #15803d;">
                Klicken Sie auf den Button, um zum Termin beizutreten ({{ virtualMeetingProvider|capitalize }}).
            </p>
            <a href="{{ virtualMeetingUrl }}" class="btn" style="background: #10b981; margin: 0;">Meeting beitreten</a>
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="action-buttons">
            <a href="{{ managementUrl }}" class="btn">Buchung verwalten</a>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
            Sollten Sie verhindert sein, bitten wir um eine rechtzeitige Stornierung.
        </p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>{{ ownerName }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

